item.description: We are trying to get some excitement generated to get out the vote. Join us at the corner of Walgreens and the China palace in downtown Rochester to wave signs for your favorite candidates.Let us know if you need a specific sign or you can hold one of our premade totems. scorpion bowls and pupu platters after 5:30.Right now we have about 8 other patriots so we could use some help.
item.name: sign wave
